# ai-tech-lead authoring repo — deterministic LF everywhere. The composer (scripts/build.*)
# emits LF; the fidelity gate compares EOL-normalized. Keeping the whole tree LF avoids CRLF
# churn between the Windows maintainer box and CI. (This governs THIS repo's working tree; the
# consumer-facing .gitattributes that ships in each dist lives at src/core/.gitattributes.)
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.ps1 text eol=lf
